item.title: Strong wind no problem for IC Windsurfers
item.author: Janice N J Pun,
item.description: On the weekend of the 14th of October, Imperial Windsurfers travelled down to Roadford lake in Devon to join the first student windsurfing festival of the academic year: Aussie Kiss 15.
